    "comment": "更新规则-示例6：多元宇宙世界内更新与切换",
    "content": "# === 示例 6: 多元宇宙 - 世界内更新与切换 (Multiverse & World Logic) ===\n  example_world_logic: |-\n    <UpdateVariable>\n        <Analysis>\n            - World Context: HOTD (Current).\n            - Event: Time passed, moved location, met Saeko.\n            - Logic: Update Local Archives, NOT Global Root.\n        </Analysis>\n        // 1. Local Updates (Time/Loc/Social)\n        _.set('Multiverse.Archives.HOTD.Time.Clock[0]', '19:00');//Local Time\n        _.set('Multiverse.Archives.HOTD.Location[0]', 'Takagi Estate');//Local Loc\n        _.set('Multiverse.Archives.HOTD.SocialWeb.Busujima_Saeko[0]', 'Trusted (Friend)');//Local Rel\n        \n        // 2. Switching World (If happens)\n        // _.set('Multiverse.CurrentWorldName[0]', 'Naruto');\n        // _.insert('Multiverse.Archives', 'Naruto', { ...init_struct... });\n    </UpdateVariable>\n\n# === 示例: 社交关系 (Object Insertion Syntax) ===\n  example_social_syntax: |-\n    <UpdateVariable>\n        <Analysis>\n            - Event: Met Bell Cranel.\n            - Action: Add to SocialWeb (Object).\n            - Syntax Check: Must use 3 arguments for _.insert.\n        </Analysis>\n        // RIGHT: Path is '...SocialWeb', Key is 'Bell_Cranel'\n        _.insert('Multiverse.Archives.Orario.SocialWeb', 'Bell_Cranel', ['Acquaintance (10)', 'White Rabbit']);//Met\n        \n        // WRONG: _.insert('...SocialWeb.Bell_Cranel', [...]);\n    </UpdateVariable>",
