    "comment": "更新规则-主体（变量快照指令）",
    "content": "【变量更新】\n在所有文本的最后，进行变量更新。\n以下是当前 **[主角状态]** 与 **[当前世界档案]** 的快照。\n**注意：** 为了节省资源，系统已自动隐藏了非当前世界的历史数据。\n\n<status_current_variables>\n<%_\n// --- EJS Context Filter System v2.0 (Multiverse Support) ---\ntry {\n    const raw = getvar('stat_data') || {};\n    const curWorldKey = raw.Multiverse?.CurrentWorldName?.[0] || 'Unknown';\n    \n    // 构建精简视图 (只包含全局 + 当前世界)\n    const filteredView = {\n        CharacterSheet: raw.CharacterSheet, // 全局面板 (必须保留)\n        CompanionRoster: raw.CompanionRoster, // 同伴列表 (保留)\n        Templates: raw.Templates, // 模板库 (必须保留用于引用)\n        Multiverse: {\n            CurrentWorldName: raw.Multiverse?.CurrentWorldName,\n            Archives: {} \n        }\n    };\n    \n    // 注入当前世界数据\n    if (raw.Multiverse?.Archives?.[curWorldKey]) {\n        filteredView.Multiverse.Archives[curWorldKey] = raw.Multiverse.Archives[curWorldKey];\n    } else {\n        filteredView.Multiverse.Archives[curWorldKey] = \"Data not initialized yet.\";\n    }\n\n    print(JSON.stringify(filteredView, null, 2));\n} catch (e) {\n    print(JSON.stringify({ error: \"EJS Filter Error\", details: e.message }));\n}\n_%>\n</status_current_variables>\n严格按照以下规则和格式进行输出，并确定每一个变量是否需要更新，不要遗漏：\n\nrule:\n  description:\n    - You should output the update analysis in the end of the next response.\n    - **In context, variable updates are omitted by the system so they are not shown to you, but you should still add it.**\n    - **CRITICAL META-RULE**: The character is unaware of the UI/Numbers. Transform data into sensory descriptions (muscle memory, instincts, physical texture).\n    - **Command Set**: `_.set` (modify), `_.insert` (add item/obj), `_.remove` (delete), `_.add` (math delta).",
