    "content": "# === 示例 8: 属性成长与数值重算 (Auto-Calc 示范) ===\n  example_stat_growth: |-\n    <UpdateVariable>\n        <Analysis>\n            - Event: Training Complete.\n            - Stat Gain: VIT +0.2, DUR +0.1.\n            - Recalculate:\n              - Old VIT=1.0, DUR=1.0 -> HP=100.\n              - New VIT=1.2, DUR=1.1.\n              - New HP Max = (1.2 + 1.1) * 50 = 115.\n              - New Stamina Max = (1.2 + MEN 1.0) * 20 = 44.\n        </Analysis>\n        // 1. Update Base Attributes\n        _.add('CharacterSheet.CoreSystem.Attributes.VIT[0]', 0.2);\n        _.add('CharacterSheet.CoreSystem.Attributes.DUR[0]', 0.1);\n        \n        // 2. Recalculate Derived Stats (MANDATORY STEP)\n        _.set('CharacterSheet.DynamicStatus.HP.MaxValue[0]', 115);//Recalc (2.3*50)\n        _.set('CharacterSheet.DynamicStatus.EnergyPools[0].MaxValue[0]', 44);//Recalc Stamina\n    </UpdateVariable>",
