    "secondary_keys": [],
    "comment": "更新规则-示例：人格/情感/关系更新",
    "content": "# === 示例: 人格·情感·关系 (Personality, Emotion & Relationship Update) ===\n  example_personality: |-\n    <UpdateVariable>\n        <Analysis>\n            - Event: Betrayed by a trusted ally. Intense anger + lingering sadness. Relationship trust drops sharply.\n            - Personality: Wariness axis shifts, new trigger pattern established.\n            - Relationship: Both local SocialWeb (world-specific) and Global deep bond need updating.\n        </Analysis>\n\n        // 1. Emotional State — immediate reaction\n        _.set('CharacterSheet.DynamicStatus.EmotionalState.Baseline[0]', -4);//Mood drop from betrayal\n        _.insert('CharacterSheet.DynamicStatus.EmotionalState.ActiveEmotions', {\n            \"emotion\": \"rage\",\n            \"intensity\": 8,\n            \"trigger\": \"ally_betrayal\",\n            \"decay\": \"slow\"\n        });//Active anger\n        _.insert('CharacterSheet.DynamicStatus.EmotionalState.RecentMoodShifts', \"Rage & grief surge — Levi's betrayal at Shinganshina\");//Log\n\n        // 2. Personality axis shift (slow drift, small delta)\n        _.add('CharacterSheet.UserPanel.Personality.Dimensions.Social.Openness[0]', -2);//Closed off\n        _.add('CharacterSheet.UserPanel.Personality.Dimensions.Values.LoyaltyExpectation[0]', 3);//Higher standard now\n\n        // 3. New trigger pattern established\n        _.insert('CharacterSheet.UserPanel.Personality.TriggerPatterns', {\n            \"trigger\": \"perceived betrayal of trust\",\n            \"reaction\": \"immediate emotional withdrawal + cold hostility\",\n            \"intensity\": 9,\n            \"decay\": \"very_slow\"\n        });//New scar\n\n        // 4a. Local SocialWeb (world-specific, simple)\n        _.set('Multiverse.Archives.AoT.SocialWeb.Levi_Ackerman[0]', 'Former Commander — trust shattered after Shinganshina');\n        _.set('Multiverse.Archives.AoT.SocialWeb.Levi_Ackerman[1]', 'hostile');\n\n        // 4b. Global deep relationship (cross-world persistent bond)\n        // First time: _.insert('SocialWeb.Relationships', { ... })\n        // Update existing: use _.set on the specific field\n        _.set('SocialWeb.Relationships[0].Trust[0]', -30);//Trust collapse\n        _.set('SocialWeb.Relationships[0].Affect[0]', -20);//Affect drop\n        _.insert('SocialWeb.Relationships[0].RecentHistory', \"Day 47: Betrayal at Shinganshina. Never forgave.\");//Record\n    </UpdateVariable>",
